---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
  { name: 'Service Providers', url: '/for-providers' },
  { name: 'Equine Facilities', url: '/for-providers/equine' }
];
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Equine Facilities on BreederHQ Marketplace"
  description="List your indoor arena, outdoor arena, round pen, boarding stalls, pasture rental, wash rack, or trail access on the BreederHQ Marketplace. $5/month, no commissions."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
<main>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-amber-50 to-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🐎</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-6">Equine Facilities</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Indoor arenas, outdoor arenas, round pens, boarding stalls, pasture rental, wash racks, and trail access.
        Owners, trainers, and riders are searching for equine facilities on the BreederHQ Marketplace.
      </p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace" class="bg-amber-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-amber-600">
        List Your Equine Facility
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">What you can list</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Riding &amp; Training Spaces</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Indoor riding arenas (covered, lit, climate options)</li>
            <li>Outdoor riding arenas with footing details</li>
            <li>Round pens for groundwork and training</li>
            <li>Wash racks with hot and cold water</li>
            <li>Trail access for guided or self-guided rides</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Boarding &amp; Pasture</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Short-term and long-term boarding stalls</li>
            <li>Pasture rental for keeping horses on your land</li>
            <li>Turnout availability and stall options</li>
            <li>Trailer parking and turnaround details</li>
            <li>Manure disposal and water access</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Why it works for equine facility owners</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📍</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Local discovery</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Riders, trainers, and clinic organizers search by location, footing, and arena dimensions. Your listing surfaces when your facility matches.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🐴</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Right-fit inquiries</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">List trailer access, footing type, jumps, lighting, and lessons-allowed status up front. Riders self-qualify before they message you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">⭐</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Reviews build trust</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Verified reviews from real riders give your facility credibility for the next inquiry.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Your listing includes</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-amber-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Subtype, indoor/outdoor, footing type, arena dimensions</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-amber-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Acreage, head capacity, stall and turnout availability</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-amber-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Trailer parking, trailer turnaround, water access, manure disposal</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-amber-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Lighting, jumps, sound system, viewing area, mounting block</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-amber-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Lessons and clinics policy, vaccination requirements, waivers</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-amber-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Photos, contact form, and inquiry-to-book workflow</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-6 text-center">
        Equine facilities use a contact-to-book workflow: riders send an inquiry, you confirm the time and arrange payment directly. No reservation calendar required.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-900 to-amber-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white"><span class="line-through opacity-60 text-2xl">$5/mo</span> Free during early access</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-amber-200 mb-3">No commissions. No per-booking fees. Cancel anytime.</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-amber-200 mb-8">Put your equine facility in front of every rider, trainer, and clinic organizer searching the marketplace.</p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace" class="bg-white text-amber-800 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-amber-50">
        List Your Equine Facility
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
